title: The Most Expensive American Planes of World War II – 24
description: World War II played a huge part in the industrial revolution within the United States as the country fully mobilized its industrial resources to out-produce its enemies. These machines of war came in the form of tanks, aircraft, and maritime vessels, and each contributed greatly to the war effort. The industrial capability was so great […]
